powertop: PowerTOP (list power consumption of software components)
powertop:
powertop: Intel is proud to announce the PowerTOP tool
powertop: (http://www.linuxpowertop.org), a program that collects the
powertop: various pieces of information from your system and presents
powertop: an overview of how well your laptop is doing in terms of
powertop: power savings. In addition, PowerTOP will provide an
powertop: indication of which tunables and software components are the
powertop: biggest offenders in slurping up your battery time. PowerTOP
powertop: will update it's display frequently so that you can directly
powertop: see the impact of any changes you are making.
